 Popular Nigerian crossdresser, Idris Okuneye, alias Bobrisky has affirmed that he will forever be a woman and nothing will make him return to being a man. The controversial crossdresser said this in a reply to a female follower who begged him to give out some shoes from his closet. This is after the drag queen shared a video of his closet and bragged that his closet is full of so many clothes and shoes that it’s almost like a boutique. “Bob incase you eventually return to man Abeg dash me small inside these shoes o. Thank you,” the follower wrote. Replying, Bobrisky wrote, “@i_am_aderonkee I’m a woman forever. Go back to man ke. God forbid.” Read Also: “I Spend So Much Money On My Friends,” Bobrisky Says As He Splashes Dollars On BBNaija’s Khloe At Her Birthday Party   A post shared by Instablog9ja (@instablog9ja) 